## Summary
This documentation details the Amplitude Activation's Intercom streaming integration, which allows forwarding Amplitude events and users to Intercom. It covers prerequisites (creating an Intercom app, obtaining access token), setup process, configuration of user ID mappings, event forwarding with property selection, and user data forwarding options.

